<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Negligence" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Negligence,</orth> 1) want of care and attention: <bibl n="shak. luc 1278" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1278</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lc 35" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 35</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.345" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 345</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.4.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 4, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.280" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 280</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.252" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 252</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.252" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 252</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.213" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 213</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.6.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 6, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 3, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.1.32" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.76" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 76</bibl>. . <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.311" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 311</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 66</bibl>.<lb />2) disregard, slight, contempt: <cit><quote>both the worlds I give to n., let come what comes; only I'll be revenged,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.134" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 5, 134</bibl></cit>.
